## Default Settings

Applied unless the track explicitly overrides:

- **Model**: V5
- **Always include in style**: voice forward, restrained, dark production, contemporary, dynamic range
- **Default Creative Sliders**: Weirdness ~35, Style Influence ~75, Audio Influence N/A (unless reference audio provided)
- **Vocals FIRST** in the style prompt (V5 weights first words highest)
- **Max 2 genre tags** in the style prompt (3+ produces inconsistent results)

