## Exclude Styles Defaults

Most tracks land with these or similar exclusions; adjust per track:

- `no autotune`
- `no aggressive vocals` (unless project-justified)
- `no maximalist production`
- `no sidechain pump`

For intimate / voice-forward tracks, also: `no drums`, `no electric guitar`.

Max **2–4 items** in the Exclude Styles section (over-specification dilutes the effect).

---

## How This Works

1. `/bitwize-music:suno-engineer` loads this file at session start
2. Genre mappings translate working vocabulary to Suno tags
3. Default settings + vocal preferences are applied unless overridden per-track
4. Avoidance rules filter out unwanted terms automatically
5. Section-tag and metatag conventions enforced (especially the voice-character / no-personal-name ban)
